query:
SELECT p.id, s.name as service_name, p.smshubPrice, p.ourPrice, a.profit_percentage 
FROM prices p 
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id 
JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id 
WHERE p.apiId = 1 AND p.smshubPrice > 0 
LIMIT 5;
